# NIFYA Backend

This document describes the structure of the NIFYA backend service.

## Key Files

- [package.json](mdc:backend/package.json) - Backend package dependencies and scripts
- [Dockerfile](mdc:backend/Dockerfile) - Docker configuration for containerization
- [cloudbuild.yaml](mdc:backend/cloudbuild.yaml) - Google Cloud Build configuration
- [README.md](mdc:backend/README.md) - Backend documentation
- [API-DOCS.md](mdc:backend/API-DOCS.md) - API documentation

## Source Code

The backend source code is organized in the [src](mdc:backend/src/) directory.

## Database

The database schema and migrations are managed in the [supabase](mdc:backend/supabase/) directory.

## Deployment

The backend is deployed to Google Cloud Run at https://backend-415554190254.us-central1.run.app.
